description:
July 16, 2018 / Fifteen years after the murder of Harold and Thelma Swain, an arrest was finally made. But not all of the investigators agree that the Camden County Sheriff’s Office got the right man. 

Episode scoring music by Blue Dot Sessions, Patrick Cortes, and Chris Zabriskie.
